takeoverEditLock.description: Clears the `locked_by` and `locked_at_timestamp`in the DRAFT version of this integration. This RPC throws an exception if the integration is not in DRAFT status or if the `locked_by` and `locked_at_timestamp` fields are not set.The TakeoverEdit lock is treated the same as an edit of the integration, and hence shares ACLs with edit.
